organization.title: Charity Commission for England and Wales
organization.description:
The Charity Commission is completely independent of ministerial influence and from charities. It is the regulator and registrar of charities in England and Wales and has a number of quasi-judicial functions where it uses powers similar to those of the High Court.

Charity Commission is a non-ministerial department

http://www.charitycommission.gov.uk/
